# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[oc]
build/
dist/
wheels/
*.egg-info
.venv

# Personal data — NEVER commit these:
# - raw.json / digest.json contain the user's name, paper-read history, etc.
# - newsletter.html embeds that data into the rendered output.
# - scholarinboxcli stores its sha_key cookie in ~/.config/scholarinboxcli/
#   (outside this repo); never copy that file into the repo.
raw.json
digest.json
newsletter.html
*.tmp.json
.env
.env.*
secrets/
config/local.*
